  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess of effect of Surgicel® (Fibrillar) for preventing delayed
      bleeding after endoscopic hemostasis in non-variceal upper gastrointestinal bleeding
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
